{"tid":1465010,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"戰場上分鬼好易","createTime":"2019-08-13T15:42:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T17:05:25.000Z","uid":81687,"like":7,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"0ace05879eba988467f906dd07892df9273c8718","tid":1465010,"uid":81687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:42:40.000Z","msg":"如果敵人落單：<br />\n打到佢仆街唔收手就係自己人<br />\n保護佢放佢走就係鬼<br />\n<br />\n唔駛猜度估裝備，1個鐘都籌到100萬美金，有人捐錢買頂級裝備有幾難<br />\n睇行動最實際，瞄空氣扮野，打無辜既人都只係&quot;可能&quot;係鬼<br />\n但保護敵人既唔駛諗一定係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46d776c39e265ad4c8b28e6714dc8494b538ccdf","tid":1465010,"uid":3696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:45:44.000Z","msg":"［正視聽］大家唔好再嘈啦<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1464495\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1464495</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"368541287f1674ef6d9a9bc7bb190ef9d38d209e","tid":1465010,"uid":57614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:46:23.000Z","msg":"結論係要引到狗入機場郁手"},{"pid":"63d022bdcfc777a3dfdde7498aa6652aae5088de","tid":1465010,"uid":16355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:47:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12f2ac0f98750758e53f24941fccb5ec6efa8bcf","tid":1465010,"uid":86837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:47:40.000Z","msg":"唔認同保護佢就係鬼"},{"pid":"2611ee429825d8a84a98887e666d31ae9cf10638","tid":1465010,"uid":267797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:47:42.000Z","msg":"唔！好！再！掛！住！捉！鬼！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔！好！俾！人！分！化！<br />\n唔該幫我推一推<br />\n［非分化］無證據咪撚亂捉鬼！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1464810\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1